edu.stanford.math.plex_plus.graph
Interface AbstractGraph

All Known Subinterfaces:
AbstractWeightedGraph
All Known Implementing Classes:
UndirectedListGraph, UndirectedWeightedListGraph
public interface AbstractGraph

This interface abstracts the functionality of an unweighted graph. The graph may be directed or undirected. The vertices of the graph are labeled {0, ..., n - 1}, where n is the number of vertices.

Author:
Andrew Tausz
